  stimulus_text = 'The speaker’s main idea is that the modern world is a place of constant change.  The speaker uses vivid imagery to emphasize the rapid pace of change, such as the idea of a “whirlwind” of events and the way “cities are born and die” within a few years.  What is the most likely reason why the speaker emphasizes this rapid pace of change? Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
